<p>This collaboration will enable us to move beyond simply improving AI performance to collectively establish a new standard for 'Wise AI' that goes beyond 'Responsible AI'. Specifically, our unique data asset and the capability to expand it are poised to play a critical role in imbuing Google Gemini models with human depth and ethical discernment, a capability difficult to achieve with conventional data. This represents the most compelling investment Google can make to solidify its ethical leadership in the AI era and contribute significantly to Google's vision of building a future where humanity and AI flourish together.</p>
</section>

